### Login Service (generates metrics)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create Product (generates metrics)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
  "name": "Sample Product",
  "description": "A sample product",
  "price": 99.99,
  "stock": 100
}

### Get Category Cache (generates cache metrics)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### Prometheus Query Examples
# Success Rate
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/query?query=rate(application_service_success_count_total[5m]) / rate(application_service_invocation_count_total[5m])

# Average Execution Time
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/query?query=rate(application_service_execution_time_seconds_sum[5m]) / rate(application_service_execution_time_seconds_count[5m])

# Error Count
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/query?query=rate(application_service_failure_count_total[5m])

# 95th Percentile Response Time
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/query?query=histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(application_service_execution_time_seconds_bucket[5m]))

